title: Why This Nurse WON'T Vaccinate!
description: I give you an few of my objections to the current practice of vaccination.  Subsequent videos will hopefully address vaccine misconceptions, the flu vaccine.  The comments are OFF for many reasons.  Foremost is that I refuse to be abused for a contrarian viewpoint that goes against mainstream "Sickcare."  This video comes at a cost to me as a practicing nurse, and the comments are a casualty of war.
